description:
An old Roman sword found in the Arctic ice!

AD68: in an unknown land a century of Roman soldiers fights an horde of barbarians from a tribe nobody saw before. The Romans had taken a long journey to unveil the secrets of the “ship people”, but maybe they were only running after a fantasy. Their fate is already sealed. 2010: a Roman sword is found in the Arctic and Martin Mystère is called to investigate about its seemingly inexplicable origin. It’s just the beginning of a dramatic adventure in the ices of the North Pole, where an ancient ship preserved from time has been waiting for centuries for its secret to resurface again…
name: Il tesoro di Didone

description: Donning high-tech battlesuits, a group of soldiers are commissioned to destroying a rogue self-operating tank in a huge city wasteland. But the machine is far more lethal than they thought...
name: Farewell to Weapons

description:
The Detective of the Impossible faces the mysteries and secrets hidden inside the KGB archives!

1945. In the woods of southern Austria, inside a seemingly deserted mine, two young men unwittingly witness a sinister event, that will doom them for the rest of their lives. 2009, Moscow. Inside the Lubjanka palace, an old German document suddenly resurfaces from the KGB archives, spreading panic in the Russian intelligence. For the first time in decades, a long-forgotten name is whispered again, and it immediately causes a shock: Arjan Bauer. A name that leaves behind itself a deadly wake, that forces Major Olga Petrovna to run, to avoid her own superior officers and former collegues, determined to make her shut up forever. Olga has no choice but asking for help to an old friend, whom she worked with in the past: Martin Mystère!
name: L’ultimo convoglio

description: The story of a young Concentration Camp survivor who was experimented on by the Nazis, so that he now transforms into a bestial creature when angered. As an adult he hunts down escaped Nazis.
Includes Steve Parkhouse and David Lloyd comic strip adaptation of the movie Quatermass II.

A menace from space and a mystery that, if solved, could save the Earth!

NEO, "Near Earth Objects" that's the name of Solar System object that could potentially strike the Earth. It's an event that happened 65 million of years ago, and that now as Professor Hogan ascertained threatens to occur again, with the same catastrophic consequences. Hogan asks Martin for help, to protect him from a group of devious characters who are on the hunt for him: they want to snatch from the Professor the shocking secret behind his discover. The Detective of the Impossible will find all the answers in Antarctica, hidden in the song of a that could cause the extinction of every life form on the Planet
name: Meteore

description: Today's battlefield isn't just about the uniformed soldier in service to his country; there's also the contractor, who answers to the corporation. Call them mercenaries, soldiers-for-hire, or private military operators, they are a new breed of combatant in today's conflicts. SHOOTERS is the story of Terry Glass, a warrior whose spirit and soul has been hardened in countless battles. When a horrible accident shatters his world, Glass finds himself waging a private war on several fronts – against his career, his marriage, and ultimately, his faith. Written by Eric S. Trautmann (CHECKMATE, Red Sonja, Flash Gordon) and Brandon Jerwa (G.I. Joe, Battlestar Galactica, Highlander), and drawn by Eisner Award-winning artist Steve Lieber (Underground, Whiteout, ROAD TO PERDITION: ON THE ROAD), SHOOTERS tells a story of modern warfare that will stay with you forever.
name: OGN

description: Batman's fallen under the hallucinogenic power of Mad Hatter's drugs...just like the kidnapped Alices he's trying to free. And it doesn't help that the drugs make them appear to be nightmarish visions out of Alice in Wonderland--and they're fighting back! How will he be able to free them and take down Mad Hatter if he's busy fighting the Jabberwocky?!
name: Vicki in Wonderland (Part 3)

description:
From a faraway future, the New Heroes join the fight again!

The world of tomorrow needs heroes! And who else can they be, if not the Alfa agents! After the defeat of the Council of Balance, the Earth government begins to create a new Agenzia Alfa and Liam, Joe and Scout will be involved again in a scheme that will take them through a thousand battles, to unveil the truth about the monster shape-changers called the Mutes and about what really happened at the end of the War of Worlds!
name: Genesi Alfa
